enough foreplay

// String indexing
moan s is "hello"
yell grab s at 0
yell grab s at 4

// String length
yell body count of s

// Split and join
moan csv is "a,b,c"
stash parts with chop csv by ","
yell grab parts at 0
yell grab parts at 1
yell grab parts at 2
yell body count of parts

// Join
moan joined is stitch parts with "-"
yell joined

// Split by empty string
stash chars with chop "hi" by ""
yell body count of chars
yell grab chars at 0
yell grab chars at 1

